<lb n="0364b09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>後出阿彌陀佛<note n="0364002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偈＋（經）【三】＊</note><note n="0364002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">偈＋（經）【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0364002"><lem wit="【大】">偈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">偈經</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0364b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0364b11" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0364003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（古舊…錄））十三字＝（（後漢失譯））【宋】，（（後漢失譯師名））【元】【明】</note><app n="0364003" cb:word-count="13"><lem wit="【大】">古舊錄云闕譯人名，今紀後漢錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">後漢失譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">後漢失譯師名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0364b12" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><lg xml:id="lgT12p0364b1201"><l>惟念法比丘，</l><l>乃從世饒王，</l>
<lb n="0364b13" ed="T"/><l>發願喻諸佛，</l><l>誓二十四章。</l>
<lb n="0364b14" ed="T"/><l>世世見諸佛，</l><l><note n="0364004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姟＝垓【宋】</note><app n="0364004"><lem wit="【大】">姟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">垓</rdg></app>數無有量；</l>
<lb n="0364b15" ed="T"/><l>不廢宿命行，</l><l>功德遂具成。</l>
<lb n="0364b16" ed="T"/><l>世界名清淨，</l><l>得佛號無量，</l>
<lb n="0364b17" ed="T"/><l>國界平夷易，</l><l>豐樂多上人。</l>
<lb n="0364b18" ed="T"/><l>寶樹若干種，</l><l>羅列叢相生，</l>
<lb n="0364b19" ed="T"/><l>本莖枝葉花，</l><l>種種各異香。</l>
<lb n="0364b20" ed="T"/><l>順風日三動，</l><l>翕習如花生，</l>
<lb n="0364b21" ed="T"/><l>墮地如手布，</l><l>雜廁上普平。</l>
<lb n="0364b22" ed="T"/><l>一切無諸山、</l><l>海水及諸源，</l>
<lb n="0364b23" ed="T"/><l>但有河水流，</l><l>音響如說經。</l>
<lb n="0364b24" ed="T"/><l>天人入水戲，</l><l>在意所欲望，</l>
<lb n="0364b25" ed="T"/><l>令水齊胳肩，</l><l>意願隨念得。</l>
<lb n="0364b26" ed="T"/><l>佛壽十方沙，</l><l>光明普無邊，</l>
<lb n="0364b27" ed="T"/><l>菩薩及弟子，</l><l>不可算稱量。</l>
<lb n="0364b28" ed="T"/><l>若欲見彼佛，</l><l>莫疑亦莫<note n="0364005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忘＝望【三】</note><note n="0364005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忘＝望【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364005"><lem wit="【大】">忘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">望</rdg></app>；</l>
<lb n="0364b29" ed="T"/><l>有疑在胎中，</l><l>不合五百年。</l>
<pb n="0364c" xml:id="T12.0373.0364c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0364c01" ed="T"/><l>不疑生<note n="0364006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">基＝臺【元】【明】</note><app n="0364006"><lem wit="【大】">基</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">臺</rdg></app>坐，</l><l>叉手無量前，</l>
<lb n="0364c02" ed="T"/><l>願欲遍十方，</l><l>須臾則旋還。</l>
<lb n="0364c03" ed="T"/><l>惟念彼菩薩，</l><l>姟劫作功勤，</l>
<lb n="0364c04" ed="T"/><l>本行如此致，</l><l>得號<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">懀<note type="cf1">K11n0190_p0175a17</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">憎</rdg></app>世尊！</l>
<lb n="0364c05" ed="T"/><l>佛興難得值，</l><l>須臾會難聞，</l>
<lb n="0364c06" ed="T"/><l>講說<note n="0364007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">士＝大【宋】【元】</note><app n="0364007"><lem wit="【大】">士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">大</rdg></app>難遇，</l><l>受學人難得。</l>
<lb n="0364c07" ed="T"/><l>若後遭末世，</l><l>法欲衰微時，</l>
<lb n="0364c08" ed="T"/><l>當共建擁護，</l><l>行佛無欲法。</l>
<lb n="0364c09" ed="T"/><l>佛能說此要，</l><l><note n="0364008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各各＝各當【三】</note><note n="0364008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各各＝各當【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364008"><lem wit="【大】">各各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">各當</rdg></app>勤思行；</l>
<lb n="0364c10" ed="T"/><l><note n="0364009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝弘【三】</note><note n="0364009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝弘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364009"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">弘</rdg></app>此無量<note n="0364010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝誓【三】</note><note n="0364010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">福＝誓【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0364010"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">誓</rdg></app>，</l><l>世世稽首行。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0364c11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>後出阿彌陀佛<app type="star" corresp="#0364002"><lem wit="【大】">偈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">偈經</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
